headline: 2 Reasons to Like JKHY (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Over the past six months, Jack Henry’s stock price fell to $150. Shareholders have lost 13.7% of their capital, which is disappointing considering the S&P 500 has climbed by 21.1%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
